{% set description %}
  An example of a Table Element with numeric data styling.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
{% spaceless %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>Refer to the <a href="{{ link['elements-table-headers-footers'] }}" class="e-bolt-text-link">Table Element with Headers and Footer</a> page for information on adding the headers and footer.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>Twig:</strong> Use the <code>format</code> prop to style the table in numeric format.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>HTML:</strong> Add a <code>e-bolt-table--numeric</code> class to the <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> to style the table in numeric format.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endspaceless %}
{% endset %}

